    "body" : "<p>This problem is not related to java, its actually something related to the way linux operates. </p>\n\n<p>You need to do following:</p>\n\n<pre><code>nohup &lt;your_application_command&gt; &amp;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note the \"nohup\" and \"&amp;\" at start and end respectively.</p>\n"
